	.index-jumbotron.container-md.p-5.text-light.text-center
		.row.pb-4.justify-content-center
			h2.display-5.fw-bold.my-2.text-light The Minecraft API
			p.col-md-8.fs-4.my-2
				| The Minecraft API is an entirely open API, which serves information about everything from blocks, to items, to dimensions and more!
